{"tid":726161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國老牌車廠被中國收購後，竟完全走向翻版之路！","createTime":"2018-07-02T07:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T17:47:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"070dd3b9ff587338050a0f691152834297615f23","tid":726161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"擁有近 100 年歷史的英國跑車廠 MG，自從被中國上海汽車集團收購後，轉為推出休旅車等熱門級距，而且完全在中國開發設計及製造，英國血統蕩然無存，近日更打算推出名為「HS」的跨界休旅，外型被許多車迷質疑抄襲 Mazda 魂動語彙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/auto/page/2018/07/02/180702-10359-35-HGiph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fauto%2Fpage%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F180702-10359-35-HGiph.jpg&h=bd586ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">MG 打算推出名為「HS」的跨界休旅，外型被許多車迷質疑抄襲 Mazda 魂動語彙。</span><br />\n<br />\n先前 MG 推出的 ZS 休旅車，就遭到車迷批評，幾乎整個外觀都是模仿 Mazda CX-5 第二代的造型，尤其是車頭部分更是如此，而即將發表的全新休旅「HS」，車頭造型竟還是繼續搭載這項設計，而且車尾與整體輪廓也被說山寨 Volkswagen 集團的風格。<br />\n<br />\n不過根據外媒《CarAdvice》報導，MG 的首席中國設計師卻表示，品牌有任何和歐系或日系車相似的地方都是無關緊要的，品牌擁有近百年的歷史，而且現在正邁向新的方向，不會管其他車迷說什麼，同時還強調，該品牌在全球有 4 設計工作室，因此外型絕對是得到全球認可的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/auto/page/2018/07/02/180702-10359-37-M6QPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fauto%2Fpage%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F180702-10359-37-M6QPG.jpg&h=22ba64ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 MG 車廠還打算回歸老本行，推出一款電動跑車，利用中國目前的電池技術打造，但是同樣在外型上，也被外媒《Motor1》指出，和 Mazda MX-5 相當類似，尤其是車頭燈和水箱護罩方面，相似度非常高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://auto.ltn.com.tw/news/10359/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fauto.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F10359%2F3&d=P5OUB97JOs26NiDkPvkxSL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=61cceef2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fauto.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F10359%2F3&h=01e828dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://auto.ltn.com.tw/news/10359/3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df451f042ad769fe2b650ab0d00997e97d24814","tid":726161,"uid":128972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"第一眼以講香港 點知係車廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0d6ea2f0e83465d692d6ca24977844f2f726e5","tid":726161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6df451f042ad769fe2b650ab0d00997e97d24814","tid":726161,"uid":128972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"第一眼以講香港 點知係車廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"一x樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d5f63dc3c10201ad2d9746c2b5d83a72755296","tid":726161,"uid":67551,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">品牌有任何和歐系或日系車相似的地方都是無關緊要的</span>，品牌擁有近百年的歷史，而且現在正邁向新的方向，<span style=\"color: red;\">不會管其他車迷說什麼</span>，同時還強調，該品牌在全球有<span style=\"color: green;\"> 4 設計工作室，因此外型絕對是得到全球認可的</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啫係話抄咪抄，唔理你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋有office數量同認受性個關聯喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人真係好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"29d82e9f2acb1aee3ad4738b2bc83e1412255bbb","tid":726161,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fee532adaf0e435b08b020f7981a432b3925490","tid":726161,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"笑左。間公司都賣左啦。人地想點都無計啦"},{"pid":"b093d8301e139ed2cd68079b265808017aa25727","tid":726161,"uid":42